platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 從遊戲中加強關鍵認知能力

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Memory, reading comprehension, concise writing—they’re valuable skills everyone can improve with this powerful brain-training app. Elevate’s short, enjoyable mini-games include activities like recalling key elements from conversations and answering true-false questions as quickly as possible. As you play a few of these games each day, the app tracks your progress and creates a personalized workout that adapts as you strengthen key abilities, helping you stay motivated over time.
Improve your memory, writing and reading comprehension with this powerful brain-training app via short, enjoyable mini games made to help strengthen key abilities and keep you motivated.
Improve your memory, writing, and reading comprehension with this powerful brain-training app via short, enjoyable mini games made to help strengthen key abilities and keep you motivated.
這款強勁的大腦訓練 App 透過簡短有趣的小遊戲，藉以提高你的記憶力、寫作和閱讀理解能力，有助增強重要能力，讓你充滿動力。

Améliorez votre mémoire, votre plume et votre compréhension écrite grâce à cette puissante app d’entraînement cérébral. Ses mini-jeux amusants vous aident à renforcer vos facultés et à garder la motivation.
